title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On March 22, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190099991 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee.
